\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 20, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rln1665702778420.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rln1665702778420.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rln1665702778420.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rln1665702778420\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Quick Search\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"rln1665702778420__quick_search_21601\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use the Quick Search box to find and replace strings in the code of the current main development object. Regular expressions are supported.\n </p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"rln1665702778420__fig_d5324e1_d5325e1_d5326e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Quick Search box in Search mode</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Quick Search box in Search mode\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/quicksearch.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"rln1665702778420__fig_d5327e1_d5328e1_d5329e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 2. </span>Quick Search box in Replace mode</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Quick Search box in Replace mode\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/quicksearch_replace.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"rln1665702778420__table_d503e1_d504e1_d505e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Quick Search Commands</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rln1665702778420__table_d503e1_d504e1_d505e1__entry__1\"> Icon</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rln1665702778420__table_d503e1_d504e1_d505e1__entry__2\"> Command </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rln1665702778420__table_d503e1_d504e1_d505e1__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rln1665702778420__table_d503e1_d504e1_d505e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"rln1665702778420__d6945e49\">\n<img alt=\"Search backwards\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/searchprev.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rln1665702778420__table_d503e1_d504e1_d505e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Search backwards</span></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rln1665702778420__table_d503e1_d504e1_d505e1__entry__3\">Search backwards. The default search\n\t\t\t\t direction is forwards.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rln1665702778420__table_d503e1_d504e1_d505e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"rln1665702778420__d6945e72\">\n<img alt=\"Match letter case\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/matchcase.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rln1665702778420__table_d503e1_d504e1_d505e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Match case</span></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rln1665702778420__table_d503e1_d504e1_d505e1__entry__3\">Find matching strings that also match the\n\t\t\t\t case of the search string.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rln1665702778420__table_d503e1_d504e1_d505e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"rln1665702778420__d6945e95\">\n<img alt=\"Match whole word\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/matchword.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rln1665702778420__table_d503e1_d504e1_d505e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Match whole word</span></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rln1665702778420__table_d503e1_d504e1_d505e1__entry__3\">Find matching strings that are preceded or\n\t\t\t\t followed by non-word characters such as spaces, commas, and periods. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rln1665702778420__table_d503e1_d504e1_d505e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"rln1665702778420__d6945e118\">\n<img alt=\"Match start of word\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/matchwordstart.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rln1665702778420__table_d503e1_d504e1_d505e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Match start of word</span></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rln1665702778420__table_d503e1_d504e1_d505e1__entry__3\">Find matching strings that are preceded by\n\t\t\t\t non-word characters such as spaces.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rln1665702778420__table_d503e1_d504e1_d505e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"rln1665702778420__d6945e141\">\n<img alt=\"Use regular expressions\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/useregexp.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rln1665702778420__table_d503e1_d504e1_d505e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Use regular\n\t\t\t\t expressions</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rln1665702778420__table_d503e1_d504e1_d505e1__entry__3\">Interpret the search string as a regular\n\t\t\t\t expression.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rln1665702778420__table_d503e1_d504e1_d505e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"rln1665702778420__d6945e166\">\n<img alt=\"Loop though the document\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/searchloop.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rln1665702778420__table_d503e1_d504e1_d505e1__entry__2\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Wrap around</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rln1665702778420__table_d503e1_d504e1_d505e1__entry__3\">When the end of the code container is\n\t\t\t\t reached, continue searching at the beginning (or the other way around, when searching\n\t\t\t\t backwards).</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rln1665702778420__topic_d2832e1_d2833e1_d2834e1_d2835e1_d2836e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d768185e250\">\n                        \n How to\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rln1665702778420__li_d2390e1_d2391e1_d2392e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yhf1665702772928.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yhf1665702772928.html\" title=\"You can search for a string or replace a string in the code editor in the Uniface IDE using the IDE code editor popup menu.\">Find and Replace Strings in Code</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531666\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531666\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Quick Search Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Quick Search Use the Quick Search box to find and replace strings in the code of the current main development object. Regular expressions are supported. Figure 1. Quick Search box in Search mode Figure 2. Quick Search box in Replace mode Table 1. Quick Search Commands Icon Command Description Search backwards Search backwards. The default search direction is forwards. Match case Find matching strings that also match the case of the search string. Match whole word Find matching strings that are preceded or followed by non-word characters such as spaces, commas, and periods. Match start of word Find matching strings that are preceded by non-word characters such as spaces. Use regular expressions Interpret the search string as a regular expression. Wrap around When the end of the code container is reached, continue searching at the beginning (or the other way around, when searching backwards). How to Find and Replace Strings in Code Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}